sub_title: Delivering a more connected, agile and sustainable future for global logistics
summary:
Helping our customers manage their global supply chains is a fantastic job. We get to work on opportunities in decarbonising logistics, creating higher standards of predictability & resilience and at the lowest possible cost. The ocean hubs of Maersk are critical to those endeavors and are the core of my current role. I lead a capital investment program for new port capacity of USD ~3bn together with a transformation program focusing on deploying advanced technology & process re-engineering.

It is a fabulous role with an amazing team who are transforming a traditional industry. That impact and our people are what get me up in the morning.
